{"tid":276192,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打去過高加索地區","createTime":"2017-06-08T15:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T16:56:19.000Z","uid":88858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d71dc0007ea0b83078b1a7ab158118314b6fddb","tid":276192,"uid":88858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"想問通常會痴埋咩國家一齊玩 e.g. Armenia, Georgia, Azerbaijan + 咩國家一齊玩<br />\n同埋azerbaijan visa 係香港有冇得整?? 定係要去到Georgia 先整到?"},{"pid":"df459ace40016836618ba5ec4738cf7b78d0e75c","tid":276192,"uid":1970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"朋友上年去左Georgia. Armenia, Iran 一路到歐洲<br />\n佢講到georgia超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望今年都有機會去到<br />\n亞塞拜疆個visa 我睇親啲blog都係話去Tbilisi 度先整"},{"pid":"82dbb2de2908339789538341c438e5435f7d8248","tid":276192,"uid":88858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友上年去左Georgia. Armenia, Iran 一路到歐洲<br />\n佢講到georgia超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望今年都有機會去到<br />\n亞塞拜疆個visa 我睇親啲blog都係話去Tbilisi 度先整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伊朗做starting point 都OK, iran 上azerbaijan, 過Georgia,落armenia 入土耳其"},{"pid":"9fd47e2a5dac59808c3a8d8130b50683a3bd3e5c","tid":276192,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"留名想去"},{"pid":"ecedd1a971a9aa9902d45e51ac71edb96ee27f55","tid":276192,"uid":71323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:02:57.000Z","msg":"Georgia睇相好靚好想去<br />\n有無人知使費貴唔貴？"},{"pid":"e333e03519c1c7a031edce95fe5319e90d56f26b","tid":276192,"uid":75439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71402e13f92b0d5f9d68a8d9725516ba790abc87","tid":276192,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:32:25.000Z","msg":"你係咪用BNO?<br />\n係既話Azeri visa係Tbilisi有tour agency搞<br />\n無記錯係150美金兩個工作天"},{"pid":"35c25ffb454721ff0c0bc375e975bb0528cabd5e","tid":276192,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Georgia睇相好靚好想去<br />\n有無人知使費貴唔貴？</blockquote><br />\n使費唔算大<br />\n我book間Airbnb都係15歐for3人<br />\n不過冇咩特別野食<br />\n但一定要飲紅酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794a1cd652ec8d042ba7630209c2ef8405061d7c","tid":276192,"uid":71323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Georgia睇相好靚好想去<br />\n有無人知使費貴唔貴？</blockquote><br />\n使費唔算大<br />\n我book間Airbnb都係15歐for3人<br />\n不過冇咩特別野食<br />\n但一定要飲紅酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n交通呢？<br />\n會唔會去山卡拉（即係靚嗰啲）地方無/少公共交通<br />\n搞到一定要join劏客tour/包車<br />\n搞到好貴？<br />\n<br />\n紅酒呢個我知<br />\n有人喺機場入境<br />\nImmigration見外國人會送支細紅酒添"},{"pid":"4ce5f1d6b7467e2a569d10e8141fc94d9b8b561f","tid":276192,"uid":75439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Georgia睇相好靚好想去<br />\n有無人知使費貴唔貴？</blockquote><br />\n使費唔算大<br />\n我book間Airbnb都係15歐for3人<br />\n不過冇咩特別野食<br />\n但一定要飲紅酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n交通呢？<br />\n會唔會去山卡拉（即係靚嗰啲）地方無/少公共交通<br />\n搞到一定要join劏客tour/包車<br />\n搞到好貴？<br />\n<br />\n紅酒呢個我知<br />\n有人喺機場入境<br />\nImmigration見外國人會送支細紅酒添</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cc89a41ef223f1209f32d45be434a5