tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/123428_ad5fde916ca98f8e706f97db39a52728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F123428_ad5fde916ca98f8e706f97db39a52728.jpg&h=f9af613a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbf6f9c6d92ece1d56be6d3fe5fcd29cc37eed5","tid":276192,"uid":55923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Georgia睇相好靚好想去<br />\n有無人知使費貴唔貴？</blockquote><br />\n使費唔算大<br />\n我book間Airbnb都係15歐for3人<br />\n不過冇咩特別野食<br />\n但一定要飲紅酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n交通呢？<br />\n會唔會去山卡拉（即係靚嗰啲）地方無/少公共交通<br />\n搞到一定要join劏客tour/包車<br />\n搞到好貴？<br />\n<br />\n紅酒呢個我知<br />\n有人喺機場入境<br />\nImmigration見外國人會送支細紅酒添</blockquote><br />\nGeorgia唔會 <br />\nArmenia呢個情況比較常見<br />\n<br />\n不過南北高加索嘅交通都係基礎級別<br />\n好多時去另一個城就用咗半日<br />\nNight train除咗某幾條路線 幾乎不存在"},{"pid":"cf0898d459786875516180ca995731d9c0429527","tid":276192,"uid":88858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Azeri有evisa<br />\n自己搞啦</blockquote><br />\n我見azerbaijan特衰可整evisa<br />\nbno格同亞美就可以免簽<br />\n<br />\n想問azer同亞美尼亞唔妥大家，會唔會入到一個入唔到第二個"},{"pid":"d468f8690c9a8740fd639ec28a17fc9a5bb2173b","tid":276192,"uid":26531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Azeri有evisa<br />\n自己搞啦</blockquote><br />\n我見azerbaijan特衰可整evisa<br />\nbno格同亞美就可以免簽<br />\n<br />\n想問azer同亞美尼亞唔妥大家，會唔會入到一個入唔到第二個</blockquote><br />\n係疆一定要經格入亞<br />\n聽過有人格入亞比人睇到張疆visa拒入<br />\n但我自己明明護照都有個疆印又無事<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地都默認晒 d遊客會經格入亞<br />\n最好經大關口"},{"pid":"d6fd9529971a0f9ab2555f578c0373dadcbb8147","tid":276192,"uid":26531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"Bagratashen 果個關口 見慣外國遊客<br />\n特區都識認 一定無問題<br />\n同埋過關要寫定紙話比關員知幾時返<br />\n每晚住咩酒店地址電話<br />\n<br />\n過左關的士落埃里溫大慨40usd"},{"pid":"fed025293f00538dcdb7754d380128ffdc8e9591","tid":276192,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/101633_07be0ddf0eb3d1b4dc3e53b00a807713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F101633_07be0ddf0eb3d1b4dc3e53b00a807713.jpg&h=7ad2c892&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n格魯吉亞近年大力發展旅遊業<br />\n成個城市已經跳左去歐洲個邊<br />\n帶bno 可以免簽<br />\n亞美尼亞就passport 落地簽<br />\n當時係伊朗冇搞到azer visa 有d 後悔<br />\n不過格+亞已經無悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n格同亞d 女人靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGeorgia妹正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係俄羅斯風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以話，三國之中GE同AM比較歐洲，AZ信回教所以比較中東"},{"pid":"9048b6d7e12ef01ed431207956613494dfce0b0d","tid":276192,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/101633_07be0ddf0eb3d1b4dc3e53b00a807713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F101633_07be0ddf0eb3d1b4dc3e53b00a807713.jpg&h=7ad2c892&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n格魯吉亞近年大力發展旅遊業<br />\n成個城市已經跳左去歐洲個邊<br />\n帶bno 可以免簽<br />\n亞美尼亞就passport 落地簽<br />\n當時係伊朗冇搞到azer visa 有d 後悔<br />\n不過格+亞已經無悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n格同亞d 女人靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGeorgia妹正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係俄羅斯風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以話，三國之中GE同AM比較歐洲，AZ信回教所以比較中東</blockquote><br />\n係因為亞同格都係天主教國家，容易接受西方文明<br />\n彊就玩鎖國得閒就打下口水戰咁樣，我既理解係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4082f10e26aea8c096265dc08fc8f8f9a862eabc","tid":276192,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Azeri有evisa<br />\n自己搞啦</blockquote><br />\n我見azerbaijan特衰可整evisa<br />\nbno格同亞美就可以免簽<br />\n<br />\n想問azer同亞美尼亞唔妥大家，會唔會入到一個入唔到第二個</blockquote><br />\n係疆一定要經格入亞<br />\n聽過有人格入亞比人睇到張疆visa拒入<br />\n但我自己明明護照都有個疆印又無事<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地都默認晒 d遊客會經格入亞<br />\n最好經大關口</blockquote><br />\n我係伊朗去亞美利亞同亞美利亞去格魯吉亞個關口都唔識特衰<br />\n亞關口半夜查左成兩粒鐘先肯出個落地簽比我<br />\n唔撚理我本bno<br />\n格魯吉亞查完話特衰唔比，之後我即時攞本bno 出黎就放人"},{"pid":"72d2bc6b9521473e234acfedca69dff11b32356f","tid":276192,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪用BNO?<br />\n係既話Azeri visa係Tbilisi有tour agency搞<br />\n無記錯係150美金兩個工作天</blockquote><br />\n伊朗德黑蘭搞好似8蚊美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ab62c5d78ef603d39da69247b8a597c604e465","tid":276192,"uid":88858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係咪用BNO?<br />\n係既話Azeri visa係Tbilisi有tour agency搞<br />\n無記錯係150美金兩個工作天</blockquote><br />\n伊朗德黑蘭搞好似8蚊美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩睇到篇文上網整evisa都係二十美金"}]}